content:
Enjoy improved formatting in the Display Text component. Have a better screen reader experience for Long Text Area, Picklist, and Data Table components. See reactive interactions in input-only fields as soon as a screen loads.

These changes apply to Lightning Experience and Salesforce Classic in Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions. Screen flow users can now:

See improved formatting when referencing Action Button or Data Table component outputs in Display Text components.
Have screen readers announce the label of Long Text Area and Picklist components when focusing on them.
Have screen readers announce when no items are selected in a Data Table component.
title: Improvements to Screen Flow Components
